1. You can use modules to make your terraform more organized.

2. Use third party modules.

3. Reuse parts of your codes.

Demo

1. Run terraform get - to get the module in .terraform folder.

2. Run terraform apply

3. Changed no of servers to 2 (as for my region no c is not supported)

4. It will spin up 3 instances with 3 security groups and install consul.
